				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The party hears the voice of the Absolute, faint, in their minds.\r\nShadowheart takes out the infernal puzzle box, it glows brighter and brighter, and then the voice stops. Player avatar questions Shadowheart about the box. If the player is not aware of Shadowheart being a Shar worshipper, then they can discover this here, if she tells them about the artefact."
				}
